subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Samantha Stosur, playing in her home country, lost her first-round match to Sorana Cirstea of Romania, 7-6 (2), 6-3, before a stunned partisan crowd at Rod Laver Arena.
